sentence: A look at the weighted underlying holdings of the First Trust Mega Cap AlphaDEX Fund (Symbol: FMK) shows an impressive 13.9% of holdings on a weighted basis have experienced insider buying within the past six months.

Home Depot Inc (Symbol: HD), which makes up 2.83% of the First Trust Mega Cap AlphaDEX Fund (Symbol: FMK), has seen 2 directors and officers purchase shares in the past six months, according to the recent Form 4 data.
The ETF holds a total of $526,575 worth of HD, making it the #13 largest holding.
